WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.750 --> 00:00:01.790
In this lesson,

00:00:01.790 --> 00:00:05.730
you learn more about building
apps that use location services.

00:00:05.730 --> 00:00:08.260
You saw how to get
a single location update,

00:00:08.260 --> 00:00:10.540
as well as how to get continuous ones.

00:00:10.540 --> 00:00:14.150
You also saw how to recognize
various activities in your device.

00:00:15.360 --> 00:00:18.510
In the next lesson,
you'll learn about geofencing.

00:00:18.510 --> 00:00:23.410
The ability to draw a virtual fence
around a location in the real world, and

00:00:23.410 --> 00:00:27.990
how to generate events when the device
enters or exits that fence.

00:00:27.990 --> 00:00:32.070
This can be used to, for example,
set a notification when you or

00:00:32.070 --> 00:00:33.650
a member of your family
has arrived home.

